
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Owner as Workflow Owner
  participant UI
  participant CP
  participant EP as Eval Workers
  participant PDP
  participant DB
  Owner->>UI: Request promote to prod
  UI->>CP: POST /v1/releases/candidates
  CP->>PDP: authorize(release.candidate.create)
  PDP-->>CP: ALLOW
  CP->>DB: Create ReleaseCandidate
  CP->>EP: Enqueue eval job
  EP->>PDP: authorize(eval.run)
  PDP-->>EP: ALLOW
  EP->>DB: Store EvalRun + results
  EP-->>CP: EvalRun complete (pass/fail)
  CP-->>UI: Show eval summary + required approver(s)
  Note over CP: MVP: minimal suite; v1: full safety/red-team/regression gates
